{"tid":1406341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我地唔試下掟雞蛋","createTime":"2019-08-04T13:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:59:07.000Z","uid":199882,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cacb46446c3b4366eeb0cbf8ea88267a41fda36","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"（轉發）全副武裝的抗暴警察，在獨裁國家是許多示威遊行者的惡夢，面對這樣的武裝，遊行示威的一方似乎是雞蛋碰石頭，但比起丟石頭，丟雞蛋似乎是更有效的武器。雞蛋破裂後的蛋汁會黏附在頭盔及透明盾牌上，更會對防護眼鏡帶來一陣模糊。若再加上水球，這種抗議方式往往會更加有力。在抗議現場，這種蛋洗戰術，能夠有效的減緩武裝警察的攻勢，畢竟看不清楚，就很難正確的推進及抓補，就算抗議者被抓，雞蛋跟水球很難說的上是致命武器。而且價格低廉，隨處可買，補充迅速。<br />\n<br />\n而且雞蛋跟水，雖然對人不具殺傷力，但對這些抗暴裝備，卻是十分的難以維護，溫度會讓濕掉的設備發黴，雞蛋腐壞的氣味會讓配戴者難以接受。而要清潔，需要大量的人力去清洗，抗議就是這麼回事，增加對方的成本，維持自己抗議的能量，不讓對方贏。<br />\n<br />\n網友加碼：在雞蛋面前，架設在路口的監視器也是難逃一劫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TWSupport/photos/a.259664934154654/2329644867156640/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTWSupport%2Fphotos%2Fa.259664934154654%2F2329644867156640%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=8tXbBdGphLRwD8DFuLHjuNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=d746340a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TWSupport/photos/a.259664934154654/2329644867156640/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n雞蛋再加遊擊戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又臭又攰死佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdcd338c6e83d6e80e80c4207e119007ff90113","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:06:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0307c26a7946b37382b3b78998a4c66f3547f13","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549ee5a0b927d46762c0e3582e8557d21bc78555","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"沒有暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deaf2035e87cd772b5cc3a55c27bd356b547b42f","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"只有暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4926ff9507c2f815808f1bab430c386667d17c09","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"Be Water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056a64a05e012362ffafb7a04851d39590802610","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"8.5 三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca379aa16d1a65f0194ef61ef2cb3afea501c4c1","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8a0bac150d47b811534b71c799175878aad72b","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:13:09.000Z","msg":"遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b953336cc5c75cc0802f721efe7c171f62eda5","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"黑警可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf6a4bab4d18990b9548cfe1b70ca57a06aa7ea","tid":1406341,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:14:22.000Z","msg":"五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25b94c994bc568b6d3f9e9a6caa124226